properties.info:
Park and Ride; these stalls are available for Park and Ride customers only. This space is reserved from 5:00am to 11:00pm and limited to stall numbers 362-562.

Daily parking; any non-reserved stalls from 1-361 is available for daily parking.  All vehicles using this facility for daily parking must register at the pay stations including those utilizing the two-hour free parking. Pay stations are located on the first floor at the bottom of both staircases.

Monthly parking is available through Diamond Parking Services Department. Diamond Parking Services can be reached by calling (206) 729-0590. They can assist you in obtaining monthly permits, arrange payment types, and set up an account for recurring monthly permits. Parking can be paid by check using monthly invoicing, or on-line by credit card.
